### Set the base URL for local testing
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8088

### Ingest a small text snippet (multipart upload)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=BOUNDARY

--BOUNDARY
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is a tiny test document for ingestion.
--BOUNDARY--

### List documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents

### Get a document by ID (replace {{docId}} with an existing ID)
@docId = REPLACE_WITH_DOCUMENT_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{docId}}

### Get chunks for a document
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{docId}}/chunks

### RAG query (adjust question and topK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is in the test document?",
  "topK": 3
}
